"title": "6611: adoption, privileges and duties of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "6611",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>As adopted members of the family of God, believers receive both the privileges and responsibilities of being children of God.</p>\n<h2>The privileges received by believers through adoption</h2>\n<h3>Believers are given the Spirit of adoption</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:6\">GAL 4:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:15\">ROM 8:15</a></p>\n<h3>Believers have access to their heavenly Father</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:18\">EPH 2:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:12\">EPH 3:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb4:16\">HEB 4:16</a></p>\n<h3>Believers become heirs with Christ of heaven</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:17\">ROM 8:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:29\">GAL 3:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:7\">GAL 4:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:12\">COL 1:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:4\">1PE 1:4</a></p>\n<h2>The benefits God gives to those he adopts</h2>\n<h3>Believers are pitied by him</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps103:13\">PSA 103:13</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Believers are protected</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:26\">PRO 14:26</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Believers are provided for</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:31-Matt6:33\">MAT 6:31–6:33</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Believers receive loving discipline</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:6\">HEB 12:6</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Believers are never forsaken</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps94:14\">PSA 94:14</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Believers are assured by the Spirit</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:16\">ROM 8:16</a></strong></p>\n<h2>The responsibilities of God's adopted children</h2>\n<h3>Believers are to walk in the light</h3>\n<p><em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:35-John12:36\">JHN 12:35–12:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:8\">EPH 5:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:4-1Thess5:5\">1TH 5:4–5:5</a></p>\n<h3>Believers are to shun evil</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor6:17-2Cor6:18\">2CO 6:17–6:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:15\">PHP 2:15</a></p>\n<h3>Believers are to purify themselves</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor7:1\">2CO 7:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:2-1John3:3\">1JN 3:2–3:3</a></p>\n<h3>Believers are to live obediently</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:50\">MAT 12:50</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:14\">1PE 1:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:2-1John5:3\">1JN 5:2–5:3</a></p>\n<h3>Believers are to live in peace</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:9\">MAT 5:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom14:19\">ROM 14:19</a></p>\n<h3>Believers are to live in love</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:13\">GAL 5:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:8\">1PE 4:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:18\">1JN 3:18</a></p>\n<h3>Believers are to be watchful</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:5-1Thess5:6\">1TH 5:5–5:6</a></p>",
